<lb n="0922a03"/>
<milestone unit="juan" n="1"/>
<lb n="0922a04"/>
<lb n="0922a05"/><head type="no">No. 1406</head><div1 type="jing">
<lb n="0922a06"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><note n="0922001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】麗本</note>佛說辟除賊害&CB00057;經</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0922a07"/>
<lb n="0922a08"/><p><note n="0922002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">南無前行元本明本俱有舊失譯人名今附東晉錄</note>南無佛南無法南無比丘僧。南無過去七佛。
<lb n="0922a09"/>南無諸佛南無諸佛弟子。南無諸師南無諸
<lb n="0922a10"/>師弟子。南無默利薛利鬼神王。禮是已便說
<lb n="0922a11"/>是&CB00057;。令我所&CB00057;皆從如願</p>
<lb n="0922a12"/><p>北方有山名<note n="0922003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">健＝犍【三】</note><note n="0922003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">健＝犍【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0922003"><lem>健</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">犍</rdg></app>陀摩訶<note n="0922004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">術＝衍【三】</note><note n="0922004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">術＝衍【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0922004"><lem>術</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">衍</rdg></app>。有鬼神王名默利
<lb n="0922a13"/><note n="0922005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">陰＝薜【元】【明】</note><app n="0922005"><lem>陰</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">薜</rdg></app>利居止彼</p>
<lb n="0922a14"/><p>有四姊弟。何等為四</p>
<lb n="0922a15"/><p type="dharani">安檀尼　閻摩尼　<note n="0922006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB04369;＝&CBa0154;【三】＊</note><note n="0922006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB04369;＝&CBa0154;【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0922006"><lem>&CB04369;</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&CBa0154;</rdg></app>摩尼　無呵尼　安
<lb n="0922a16"/>檀尼　令賊目盲　<note n="0922007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">無訶＝閻摩【三】</note><note n="0922007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">無訶＝閻摩【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0922007"><lem>無訶</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">閻摩</rdg></app>尼　令賊住　<app type="＊" source="0922006"><lem>&CB04369;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&CBa0154;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0922a17"/>摩尼　令賊坐　無呵尼　令賊愚癡　癡如
<lb n="0922a18"/>是　漚羅利　無羅利　壇坻遮　波頭摩
<lb n="0922a19"/>　遮迦利　當使賊　口齒噤　至解縷　乃得
<lb n="0922a20"/>脫</p>
<lb n="0922a21"/><p>說如是&CB00057;已。便言我為某甲若干人等。作擁
<lb n="0922a22"/>護辟邪害皆令得安隱</p>
<lb n="0922a23"/><p>始諷誦是經時。當用月二十九日。於佛前然
<lb n="0922a24"/>七燈燒。膠香散花說。是&CB00057;七<note n="0922008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">過＝遍【三】＊</note><note n="0922008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">過＝遍【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0922008"><lem>過</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">遍</rdg></app>并。&CB00057;願默
<lb n="0922a25"/>利羅鬼神王使得福德亦。為然燈燒香<note n="0922009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔散〕－【宋】</note><app n="0922009"><lem>散</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>花
<lb n="0922a26"/>復為鬼子母然七燈燒香散花亦。當說是經
<lb n="0922a27"/>七<app type="＊" source="0922008"><lem>過</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">遍</rdg></app>後。&CB00057;乃<note n="0922010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">告＝吉【三】</note><note n="0922010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">告＝吉【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0922010"><lem>告</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">吉</rdg></app>當如是語即。從如願</p>
<lb n="0922a28"/><juan fun="close" n="001"><jhead><note n="0922011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">末題新加</note>佛說辟除賊害&CB00057;經</jhead></juan></div1>
